messages.content: Hi there! This is Sarah from DreamSeed. What's your full name?
My name is John Smith and I want to start a tech consulting LLC in Texas.
It's john.smith@techconsult.com and this is very urgent - I need to launch in 30 days.
Perfect! What type of business are you starting?
I'm starting TechConsult Pro LLC to help restaurants implement AI solutions. I'll be working with local businesses in Dallas.
Excellent! What's your timeline for getting started?
I need this done ASAP. I have 3 clients ready to sign contracts worth $50k total once I get my LLC paperwork done.
